      "num": "01 · the shape",
      "heading": "The schema is only half the change",
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "prose",
          "html": "<p class=\"body\">Real migrations touch code, data, jobs, queries, dashboards, and rollback assumptions. The risky part is often the period where old and new shapes both exist.</p>"
        },
        {
          "type": "terminal",
          "title": "db · expand contract",
